      "body" : "I suggest that the <code>ln</code> command should be <code>sudo ln -sfn $HOMEBREW_PREFIX&#47;opt&#47;openjdk&#47;libexec&#47;openjdk.jdk &#47;Library&#47;Java&#47;JavaVirtualMachines&#47;openjdk.jdk</code>, since the default <code>HOMEBREW_PREFIX</code> is different between arm and x64 macos systems. And it&#39;s user-configurable too."
