    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As an add-on to the accepted answer: to install a certain version of Java, e.g. version 11, run:</p>\n<pre><code>brew install openjdk@11\n</code></pre>\n<p>And symlink it:</p>\n<pre><code>sudo ln -sfn /opt/homebrew/opt/openjdk@11/libexec/openjdk.jdk \\\n     /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/openjdk-11.jdk\n</code></pre>\n"
