    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use <a href=\"https://www.jenv.be\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">jenv</a> + Homebrew on macOS:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>brew install jenv</code></li>\n<li>Configure Zsh (use other instructions here if applicable <a href=\"https://www.jenv.be\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://www.jenv.be</a>)\n<ul>\n<li><code>echo 'export PATH=&quot;$HOME/.jenv/bin:$PATH&quot;' &gt;&gt; ~/.zshrc</code></li>\n<li><code>echo 'eval &quot;$(jenv init -)&quot;' &gt;&gt; ~/.zshrc</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>eval &quot;$(jenv init -)&quot;</code> (initialize jenv)</li>\n<li><code>brew install openjdk@23</code> (or the version you want)</li>\n<li><code>jenv add /opt/homebrew/opt/openjdk@23/libexec/openjdk.jdk/Contents/Home/</code></li>\n<li><code>jenv global openjdk64-23.0.1</code> (set global java version)</li>\n<li>restart shell</li>\n</ul>\n"
